2015年8月22日，格里兹曼在馬競新賽季首場主場比賽中打進全場唯一進球，協助馬競以1:0擊敗升班馬[[拉斯帕尔马斯竞技联盟|拉斯帕尔马斯]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Atl Madrid 1–0 Las Palmas|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34011857|accessdate=2015-08-23|date=2015-08-22|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825014454/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34011857|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在同年9月15日再打進一球，協助馬競在[[2015–16年欧洲冠军联赛|2015–16年歐洲冠軍聯賽小組賽]]擊敗[[加拉塔沙雷體育會|加拉塔沙雷]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Yilmaz|first1=Cetin Cem|title=Griezmann leads Atlético to Galatasaray win|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000634/match=2015669/postmatch/report/|accessdate=2015-10-13|publisher=UEFA|date=2015-09-15|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021080317/http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000634/match=2015669/postmatch/report/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 一星期後，他在馬競對陣同城俱樂部[[赫塔費足球俱樂部|赫塔費]]的比賽中梅開二度並協助床單軍團登上西甲榜首。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Walker|first1=Joseph|title=Antoine Griezmann superb as Atletico Madrid beat Getafe, go top of La Liga|url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/atletico-madrid/1068/blog/post/2625734/antoine-griezmann-superb-as-atletico-madrid-beat-getafe|accessdate=2015-10-13|publisher=ESPN|date=2015-09-22|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008091459/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/atletico-madrid/1068/blog/post/2625734/antoine-griezmann-superb-as-atletico-madrid-beat-getafe|dead-url=no}}</ref> 10月18日，格里兹曼面對老東家皇家社會，他在第9分鐘面對門將[[傑羅尼莫·魯利|傑羅尼莫·魯利]]採取勺子射門協助馬競2:0擊敗對手。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Rogers|first1=Iain|title=Real Sociedad 0-2 Atletico Madrid: Antoine Griezmann and Yannick Ferreira-Carrasco pile misery on David Moyes' nine-man side|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3278123/Real-Sociedad-0-2-Atletico-Madrid-Antoine-Griezmann-Yannick-Ferreira-Carrasco-pile-misery-David-Moyes-nine-man-side.html|accessdate=2015-10-18|work=每日郵報|agency=Reuters|date=2015-10-18|archive-date=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019013446/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3278123/Real-Sociedad-0-2-Atletico-Madrid-Antoine-Griezmann-Yannick-Ferreira-Carrasco-pile-misery-David-Moyes-nine-man-side.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

